1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,320
Here the session has already started, and the voice area
is ready without making the whole app feel like a control
panel.

2
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:16,330
One tap enables speak and auto-send. Then continuous voice
mode and spoken replies keep the loop going with less
keyboard friction.

3
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:25,600
After the user speaks, Mano Vaarta can answer aloud and
keep the next turn ready. That makes it feel closer to a
guided conversation.

4
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:33,500
The point is not flashy voice AI. It is a calmer
hands-free check-in for moments when typing feels like
extra work.
